SELECT DISTINCT v.orderDate
                ,sdVisits

            FROM `temp.attri_Orders`
            WHERE orderDate >= '2022-08-01'
            ) a
        
        GROUP BY orderDate
        ) ord
ON v.orderDate = ord.orderDate

","temp.allData")

paragraphs.title: Monthly_Seo_Cat_Visits
paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT DISTINCT month
                ,v.categoryId
                ,categoryName
                ,seoVisits
FROM(
    SELECT SUBSTR(orderDate,1,7) AS month
            ,categoryId
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.sessionId) AS seoVisits
    FROM(
        SELECT *
        FROM `temp.visitChannel`
        WHERE LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%seo%'
            AND orderDate >= '2022-08-01'
        ) v
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT pogId
                            ,sessionId
                            ,categoryName
                            ,categoryId
            FROM `last240Days(productView)`
            ) pv
    ON v.sessionId = pv.sessionId
    
    GROUP BY SUBSTR(orderDate,1,7)
            ,categoryId
    ) v

LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT categoryId
                        ,categoryName
        FROM `all(dProduct)`) dp
ON v.categoryId = dp.categoryId
ORDER BY month DESC, categoryName ASC
",1000)

paragraphs.title: Monthly_Seo_Cat_Visits_Dup
paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT DISTINCT month
                ,v.categoryId
                ,categoryName
                ,seoVisits
FROM(
    SELECT SUBSTR(orderDate,1,7) AS month
            ,categoryId
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT v.sessionId) AS seoVisits
    FROM(
        SELECT *
        FROM `temp.visitChannel`
        WHERE LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%seo%'
            AND orderDate >= '2022-08-01'
        ) v
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT pogId
                    ,sessionId
                    ,categoryName
                    ,categoryId
            FROM(
                SELECT DISTINCT pogId
                                ,sessionId
                                ,categoryName
                                ,categoryId
                                ,guid
                                ,timestamp
                                ,row_number() over(partition by guid order by timestamp asc) as rn
                FROM `last240Days(productView)`
                )
            WHERE rn=1
            ) pv
    ON v.sessionId = pv.sessionId
    
    GROUP BY SUBSTR(orderDate,1,7)
            ,categoryId
    ) v

LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT categoryId
                        ,categoryName
        FROM `all(dProduct)`) dp
ON v.categoryId = dp.categoryId
ORDER BY month DESC, categoryName ASC
",1000)

paragraphs.title: Monthly_Seo_Cat_Orders
paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT ord.month
        ,categoryId
        ,categoryName
        ,SUM(seoOrders) AS seoOrders

FROM(
    SELECT SUBSTR(orderDate,1,7) AS month
            ,subCategoryId
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId) AS seoOrders
    FROM(
        SELECT *
        FROM `temp.attri_Orders`
        WHERE orderDate >= '2022-08-01'
            AND Channel = 'SEO'
        ) atb
    
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT pogId
                            ,subOrderId
                            ,categoryGroup
                            ,subCategoryId
            FROM `all(agCmDump)`
            ) ag
    ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
    
    GROUP BY SUBSTR(orderDate,1,7)
            ,subCategoryId
    ) ord

LEFT JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT subCategoryId
                        ,categoryId
                        ,categoryName
        FROM `all(dProduct)`
        ) dp
ON ord.subCategoryId = dp.subCategoryId

GROUP BY ord.month
        ,categoryId
        ,categoryName

ORDER BY month DESC, categoryName ASC
",1000)

with t1 as(

select h.orderDate
        ,h.deviceType
        ,h.orderId
        ,case when order=0 then 'whatsapp' 
            when order=1 then 'SEO' end as Channel
        ,sb.subOrderId
        ,sb.subOrderCode 
from(
    select orderDate
            ,deviceType
            ,orderId
            ,min(order) as order 
    from(
        select distinct to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((createdDate) / 1000)) as orderDate
                        ,deviceType
                        ,orderId
                        ,case when Channel='whatsapp' then 0 
                            else 1 end as order 
        from(
            select distinct b.createdDate,
                            Channel,
                            b.deviceType,
                            b.orderId,
                            time
            from `last365Days(saleOrder)` b
            join (
                select distinct r.deviceType,
                                lastGuid as guid,
                                startTime as time,
                                case  when lower(sessionFirstChannel) like '%seo%' then 'SEO'
                                else 'Others' end as Channel
                from `last365Days(sessionSummary)` r
                where(lower(lastGuid) not like '%default%')
                ) c 
            on c.guid = b.guid
            and c.time + 86400000 > b.createdDate
            and b.createdDate > c.time and lower(b.statusCode) NOT LIKE '%fld%' and Channel!='Others'
   

            union
            
            
            select distinct b.createdDate,
                            Channel,
                            b.deviceType,
                            b.orderId,
                            time
            from `last365Days(saleOrder)` b
            
            join(
                select distinct r.deviceType,
                                lastGuid as guid,
                                startTime as time,
                                case when lower(utmCampaign) like '%transact_whatsapp%' 
                                    or lower(utmCampaign) like '%toofani_inline%' 
                                    or lower(utmCampaign) like '%toofani_wa_men%' 
                                    or lower(utmCampaign) like '%wa_vip_promotion%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%cta_whatsapp_%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%toofani_target_%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%toofani_men%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%appinstall_wamsite%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%wa_promotion_msg1%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%app_install_msite%' 
                                    or lower(utmCampaign) like '%transact_toofani%'
                                    or lower(utmCampaign) like '%transact_after_sale_end%'  
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%cta_toofani%'  
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%cta_after_sale_end%'
                                    or lower(utmContent) like '%transact_whatsapp%' 
                                    or lower(utmContent) like '%toofani_inline%' 
                                    or lower(utmContent) like '%toofani_wa_men%' 
                                    or lower(utmContent) like '%wa_vip_promotion%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%cta_whatsapp_%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%toofani_target_%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%toofani_men%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%appinstall_wamsite%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%wa_promotion_msg1%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%app_install_msite%' 
                                    or lower(utmContent) like '%transact_toofani%'
                                    or lower(utmContent) like '%transact_after_sale_end%'  
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%cta_toofani%'  
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%cta_after_sale_end%'
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%wa_retention%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%whatsapp_retention%'         
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%whatsapp_d0%' 
                                    or lower(utmSource) like '%whatsapp_promotional%' 
                                    or lower(utmCampaign) like '%whatsapp_promotional%' then 'whatsapp'
                                else 'Others' end as Channel
                from `last365Days(sessionSummary)` r
                where(lower(lastGuid) not like '%default%')
                ) c 
                on c.guid = b.guid
                and c.time + 604800000 > b.createdDate
                and b.createdDate > c.time and lower(b.statusCode) NOT LIKE '%fld%' and Channel!='Others'
   
            )k
        )i 
    group by orderDate
            ,deviceType
            ,orderId

    )h 
left join `last365Days(suborder)` sb 
on sb.orderId=h.orderId

                )






select distinct orderDate
                ,case when Channel in ('Affiliates','Criteo','Affiliate') then 'Criteo_and_affiliates'
                    when Channel is null then 'UnattributedUTM'
                    when Channel='FacebookPaid' then 'Facebook Paid'
                    when Channel='GooglePaid' then 'Google Paid'
                    when Channel='Direct_AppShare' then 'Direct'
                    else Channel end as Channel
                ,orderId
                ,order_f as shipped_orderId
                ,subOrder_f as shipped_suborder
                ,deviceType
                
from(
    select distinct ag.orderId as order_f
                    ,ag.subOrderId as subOrder_f 
                    ,seven.* 
    from(
        select distinct case when orderDateA is null then orderDateB 
                            else orderDateA end as orderDate,

                        case when orderIdA is null then orderIdB 
                            else orderIdA end as orderId,
                        
                        case when subOrderCodeA is null then subOrderCodeB 
                            else subOrderCodeA end as subOrderCode,
                        
                        case when Channel is null then sessionFirstChannel 
                            else Channel end as Channel,
                        
                        case when deviceTypeA is null then deviceTypeB 
                            else deviceTypeA end as deviceType,
                        
                        case when subOrderIdA is null then subOrderIdB 
                            else subOrderIdA end as subOrderId

        from(
        
        select five.orderDate as orderDateA
                ,four.orderDate as orderDateB
                ,five.orderId as orderIdA
                ,four.orderId as orderIdB
                ,five.subOrderCode as subOrderCodeA
                ,four.subOrderCode as subOrderCodeB
                ,five.deviceType as deviceTypeA
                ,four.deviceType as deviceTypeB
                ,five.sessionFirstChannel
                ,four.Channel

                ,four.subOrderId as subOrderIdB
        from(
            SELECT DISTINCT to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((c.createdDate) / 1000)) AS orderDate,

                            c.orderId,

                            c.subOrderId,
